Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐 这里不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.70,0:01:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有人来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关...关羽姐 在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 小孔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.83,0:02:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为答应了要把那本书借给小孔的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德 你到底是怎么看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四话 视卒如婴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...关羽前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我是一年级的周仪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.52,0:03:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直很尊敬前辈的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请...请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐的礼物害得我都胖了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:03:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼德你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 老头子在叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水镜老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给木造物驱虫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在要去买酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们总要做这种脏累活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水镜老师去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐 从刚才开始就一直走神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲谋 马上就到成都学院了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一又和上次一样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多说无用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了不变成那样才要办和好会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:04:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:04:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过刘备玄德大人真的是位很好的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们带上便当 来开和好会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家的家计...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的因为便当的费用就...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是社交舞的授业时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到那个老师是我喜欢的肌肉型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作又增加了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这好像真的是个宝贝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:05:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对...对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢...丢死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 被你这么粗犷的手碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家害羞得做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着和你完全不配的项链
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡闹什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行啊 关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为女子 不可以用那么粗暴的说话方式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会坐在地上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不记得刚才的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的事情是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是心露石做的项链
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心露石是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上它的人会暴露本性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是恐怖的魔石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,察觉出佩戴者内心深处的夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配佩戴者的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在摸什么啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HI BABY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要摆出这么可怕的脸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 翼德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他带上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HI 张飞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.98,0:07:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想和你来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是黄忠的本性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是个花和尚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦耶 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始两个人来享受一下我的技巧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我适可而止 白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳头还是那么厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想被打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HI 关羽姐 胸部颤颤的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然关羽姐与本大爷更合适
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HI BABY 今天我要好好摸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我去死吧 花和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南无南无
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...这是最后的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约好给你的书
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.07,0:09:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德  果然你...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始关羽姐就一直走神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没有发烧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.20,0:09:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走...要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去后山大树下看书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子 喜欢看书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张飞也是老样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会胖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管闲事 你找打哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 请不要打我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 要打
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快救我 小孔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比我还...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 小孔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想知道玄德的真正心意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她到底是怎么看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐 关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你今天很奇怪呢 关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没...没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 不去吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上它的人会暴露本性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,察觉出佩戴者内心深处的夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配佩戴者的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:11:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心露石项链不能就这么放着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.82,0:11:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一被谁得到有可能会再次引起麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 黄忠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去吃饭的这段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看守好那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 我来看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孔真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里睡着 会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时就先这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孔 身上有着婴儿般的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道 好想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就活不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道 想知道 想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 让你请我吃什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我请客吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.88,0:12:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸了别人你好意思不赔罪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是南阳的...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 小孔醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德的胸部好大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.89,0:12:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的梦话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关羽姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.77,0:12:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为闻到了关羽姐的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的味道？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的味道 味道 味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...想送你做礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你这样看着 我会害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这个项链闪闪的 真的好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 快带上看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎...怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.55,0:13:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 心情有没有惴惴不安...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 很想沉浸在书里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说想对我说些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许有点闷热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.71,0:13:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是不喜欢的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.11,0:13:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚...刚刚你说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 关羽姐 我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我也喜欢小孔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有张飞和子龙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家我都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐也带上看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很适合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.96,0:14:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.74,0:14:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HI 来客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小刘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙策小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙策伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:14:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来捣乱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么站在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用看护了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是刚才的...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.35,0:15:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么关羽姐戴着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.36,0:15:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 关羽姐 你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听见了当家的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐把玄德给带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是心露石项链的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子龙 那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子龙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是赵云子龙的本性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼 关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我换衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在桃园立誓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会变成这样的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是关羽姐 今天不是练武的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子龙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你们两个人都要陪我练武吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很高兴 不过好为难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那个项链有那么不可思议的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说这个的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个要是真正打起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.98,0:16:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不能全身而退啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一定是哪一方会丢掉性命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么不吉利的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切磋虽然是可以的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然对我们的当家无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子龙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德是不会交给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想拆散我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就等着丧命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐 你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了让你闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去阻止看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 公瑾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么两个一定要争斗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老头子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 事情变得这么麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.23,0:18:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对当家做出了这么不敬的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早已有所觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不允许自己剥夺自己性命的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙子曰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视卒如婴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对待士兵要像对待婴儿般爱护
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.90,0:19:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于当家来说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵们就像是婴儿一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以当家的总是要深思熟虑考虑一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽姐要是死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道谁会最难过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我作为当家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要知道你和子龙两个人争斗的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...那是因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是因为这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:19:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上这个项链
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会无意识地陷入打斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.64,0:20:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙策伯符 你...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔力很非常强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我带上的时候什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙策小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 小刘 今天是和好日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和好日的话 我应该告诉你的是下周啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 这种事情当然是越早越好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.18,0:20:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...吕蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一天都为我浪费掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:21:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管今天有没有成果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.16,0:21:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直失忆下去并不是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 吕蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果恢复了记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙又会变成以前的吕布奉先
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完饭再回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把她交给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 小蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.07,0:21:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.73,0:23:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.64,0:23:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的突然到访 没有给您添麻烦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.67,0:23:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.34,0:23:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲谋来了以后 每天都好开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.74,0:23:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲谋才是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.69,0:23:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我们在一起 有没有觉得好辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.94,0:23:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者好累呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.07,0:23:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想知道仲谋的真心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.51,0:23:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 用这个项链的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.20,0:23:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙策小姐 不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个已经...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.46,0:23:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙权小姐？孙权小姐她...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 仲谋原来是这样的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.12,0:23:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五话 非危不战
